PrecisAmendment to the NATIONAL HISTORIC PARKS ADMISSION FEES REGULATIONS, 1989 deleting from the short title the date "1989", clarifying the definition of "sponsored group", raising admission fees at Fort George, Battle of the Restigouche and Fort Chambly National Historic Parks, bringing them closer to the higher fees charged at similar attractions in the region.
